  <brief_title>Two or Five cm From Pylorus During Laparoscopic Sleeve Gastrectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparative Study Between Two and Five cm Resection During Laparoscopic Sleeve Gastrectomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
